Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Labor Day parades end
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043xql1
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 7 Sep 1986
Reagan's stand on air traffic controllers' strike blamed for loss of labour union power which has seen membership fall dramatically. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less